{
  "stem": "17606.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And other-- and were sent to regular battalion where they had to serve 18 months instead of-- instead of 12.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they found all kind of excuses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I graduated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't so easy to get through that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suffered quite a-- quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Emotionally.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Physically, I could take everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Emotionally was much, much harder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They let me know on every step of the way that I'm a Jew, a stranger from them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot be a professional officer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why am I-- so I said, who cares?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have soup at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we call them-- they're going for soup, they become professional-- they're soldiers for the soup.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say, I have soup at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with many things, especially on Sundays we felt it the most.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sunday morning, they lined up the battalion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The school was called a battalion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they lined it up to go to church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the corporal who hardly knew how to write his own name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Didn't know even how to speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was-- used to-- to play a game of words said of [SPEAKING POLISH], Jewish believe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, [POLISH] lover, step out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I didn't budge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My two friends stepped out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They know it meant them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was all kind of this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Next day, I was taken to a battalion, this report, and I was saying the report was not to me and the order was not given to me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I am a-- a corporal with the-- this, for the census.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And not a-- was not a [POLISH] lover.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I am [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I didn't take.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course, they bowled me out a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the-- the hell the corporal got, on-- or the-- the platoon-- platoon leader.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was so many occasions like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
